            . I am a <rs id="t18150913-97-viclabel547" type="occupation">hosier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-97-victim909 t18150913-97-viclabel547"></join> and <rs id="t18150913-97-viclabel548" type="occupation">glover</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-97-victim909 t18150913-97-viclabel548"></join>; I have a shop on <placeName id="t18150913-97-crimeloc549">Ludgate-hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150913-97-crimeloc549" type="placeName" value="Ludgate-hill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18150913-97-crimeloc549" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-97-off545 t18150913-97-crimeloc549"></join>, and another in the Strand. On the 20th of August, suspecting all was not right, I followed the prisoner out my house on Ludgate-hill, into the Strand. I requested him to walk into my shop in the Strand, and on searching him in my bed-room, I found two pair of kid gloves in his side pocket, and four pair of silk gloves in the back part of his trowsers. I sent for an officer, and had him taken into custody.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150913-97-person911">
